  "text": "The proposed numerical integration scheme is applied in the following cases of SC cable arrangements in homogeneous ground. First the case of a shallowly located SC cable system of Fig. 2 is examined [CITATION_1] in a horizontal (Fig. 2a) and a vertical (Fig. 2b) Fig. 2 . The conductivity of the air is considered to be zero.",
